    <div class="column-1">
      <h2 class="gem-c-heading  gem-c-heading--padding gem-c-heading--border-top-5 brand--civil-service brand__border-color">Civil Service Diversity & Inclusion</h2>


      <div class>
          <div class>
              <div class="gem-c-image-card  brand--civil-service">
    <figure class="gem-c-image-card__image-wrapper"><img class="gem-c-image-card__image" alt="Champion Difference logo" src="https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/promotional_feature_item/image/51/D_and_I_final_logo.jpg"></img></figure>

    <div class="gem-c-image-card__text-wrapper">
      


      <div class="gem-c-image-card__description">The Civil Service is a modern and diverse workplace reflecting the communities we serve, with an ambition to become the UK’s most inclusive employer by 2020, where people are able to bring their whole selves to work and perform at their best.</div>

        <ul class="gem-c-image-card__list gem-c-image-card__list--indented">
            <li class="gem-c-image-card__list-item">
              <a class="gem-c-image-card__list-item-link brand__color" href="https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/civil-service/about/equality-and-diversity">Visit our Equality and Diversity page</a>
            </li>
            <li class="gem-c-image-card__list-item">
